Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with logical characterizations and new classes of decidable logics.
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is also likely as the paper discusses automata for finite words over an infinite alphabet.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper deals with closure and decidability properties.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility as the paper deals with expressing relations between component values.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possibility as the paper discusses decidability results.
